            <title xml:id="name520-2" xml:lang="fr-x-bhsyre" source="#bib520-1">ʾŌr</title>
            <title xml:id="name520-3" xml:lang="fr" source="#bib520-1">De Ôr</title>
            <title xml:id="name520-4"
                   xml:lang="en"
                   source="#bib520-1"
                   syriaca-tags="#syriaca-headword">On Or</title>
            <author xml:lang="fr" source="#bib520-1">Jérôme et Enanicho</author>
            <author xml:lang="en" source="#bib520-1">Jerome and Enanisho</author>
            <note xml:lang="syr" type="incipit" source="#bib520-1">
               <quote>ܚܙܝܢܢ ܬܘܒ ܓܒܪܐ ܚܕ ܬܡܝܗܐ: ܕܫܡܗ ܐܒܐ ܐܘܪ: ܐܒܐ ܕܐܚ̈ܐ ܕܝܪ̈ܝܐ ܐܠܦ...</quote>
            </note>
            <note xml:lang="fr" type="incipit" source="#bib520-1">
               <quote>Nous vîme encore un homme admirable qui s’appelait Abba Ôr, père de mille frères moines…</quote>
            </note>
            <note xml:lang="syr" type="explicit" source="#bib520-1">
               <quote>ܚܙܿܐ ܗܘ̣ܐ ܕܝܢ ܐܢܫ ܠܟܢܫܐ ܕܝܚܝ̈ܕܝܐ ܕܥܡܗ ܒܥܕܬܐ: ܐܝܟ ܓܘܕܐ ܕܟ̈ܐܢܐ: ܕܒܠܒܘ̈ܫܐ ܡܦܪܓܝܢ: ܘܒܬܫ̈ܒܚܬܐ ܐܡܝ̈ܢܬܐ ܠܐܠܗܐ ܡܫܒܚܝܢ.</quote>
            </note>
            <note xml:lang="fr" type="explicit" source="#bib520-1">
               <quote>On voyait la congrégation des solitaires avec lui dans l’église, comme un choeur de justes, aux vêtements resplendissants glorifier Dieu de louanges éternelles.</quote>
            </note>
            <note type="editions">
               <bibl source="#bib520-1">
                  <author n="1">Bedjan, P.</author>
                  <title n="1">Acta Martyrum et Sanctorum Syriace 7</title>
                  <citedRange n="1">p. 358-362</citedRange>
               </bibl>
            </note>
            <note type="editions">
               <bibl source="#bib520-1">
                  <author n="2">Budge, E. A. W.</author>
                  <title n="2">The Book of Paradise, being the Histories and Sayings of the Monks and Ascetics of the Egyptian Desert by Palladius, Hieronymus and others (Lady Meux Manuscript, 6) 2</title>
